OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775401882
OL,3,CDublin man faces extradition to NI for
OL,4,CBelfast murder
OL,6,FA man has appeared in court facing
OL,7,Fextradition in relation to the murder
OL,8,Fof Dublin criminal Robbie Lawlor in
OL,9,FBelfast six years ago.
OL,11,FJonathan Gill, 44, of Malahide Road in
OL,12,FClontarf, appeared before the High
OL,13,FCourt in Dublin after being arrested
OL,14,Fon foot of an extradition warrant.
OL,16,FHe is facing charges for the murder of
OL,17,FMr Lawlor and alleged possession of a
OL,18,F9mm pistol between April 2 and 5 2020.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
