OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775401882
OL,3,CDublin man faces extradition to NI for
OL,4,CBelfast murder
OL,6,FMr Lawlor was shot on Etna Drive in
OL,7,Fthe Ardoyne area of Belfast on April 4
OL,8,F2020.
OL,10,FHe had been linked to the murder of
OL,11,FLouth teenager Keane Mulready-Woods,
OL,12,Fwho was dismembered with parts of his
OL,13,Fbody dumped across Dublin in 2020.
OL,15,FAn Garda Siochana are investigating
OL,16,Fthe murder of Mr Lawlor jointly with
OL,17,Fthe PSNI and arrested Gill on Thursday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
