PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775401882
OL,3,CDublin man faces extradition to NI for
OL,4,CBelfast murder
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Frank Lambe, from
OL,7,Fthe extradition unit at the Garda
OL,8,Fnational bureau of criminal
OL,9,Finvestigation, told the High Court on
OL,10,FFriday he had arrested Gill, also
OL,11,Fknown as Jack Gill, in Clontarf at
OL,12,F4.50pm on Thursday.
OL,14,FThe officer identified himself and his
OL,15,Frank to Gill, who made no reply when
OL,16,Fcautioned, the court heard.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
