OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775401882
OL,3,CDublin man faces extradition to NI for
OL,4,CBelfast murder
OL,6,FDet Sgt Lambe said Gill was taken to
OL,7,FClontarf Garda Station where he was
OL,8,Fshown the warrant for his arrest,
OL,9,Fendorsed by the High Court in Dublin,
OL,10,Fand asked him to confirm his name and
OL,11,Fdate of birth.
OL,13,FHe was informed of his right to legal
OL,14,Frepresentation, a right to a
OL,15,Ftranslator and a right to legal advice
OL,16,Fin the UK.
OL,18,FMr Lambe said a summary of the
OL,19,Foffences was read to Gill and he was
OL,20,Fasked if he knew "what the offences
OL,21,Fare about", "to which he replied 'no'."
OL,26,@|D@ROU}D@JO]}D@MOU}D@gO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775401882
OL,3,CDublin man faces extradition to NI for
OL,4,CBelfast murder
OL,6,FMr Lambe said he was satisfied the
OL,7,Fperson on the warrant was the same
OL,8,Fperson before the High Court on Friday
OL,9,Fmorning, and identified Gill in the
OL,10,Fcourtroom as the man dressed in a
OL,11,Fblack top and shorts.
OL,13,FJudge Mr Justice Barry O'Donnell said
OL,14,Fhe was "clearly satisfied" as to
OL,15,FGill's identity.
OL,17,FHe then informed Mr Gill of his rights
OL,18,Fagain and asked Gill if he understood
OL,19,Fthose rights.
OL,21,FMr Gill replied "yes" to the judge.
OL,26,@vD@HOUvD@ZO]}D@QOU}D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
