CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775401882
OL,3,CDublin man faces extradition to NI for
OL,4,CBelfast murder
OL,6,FDefence barrister Gemma McLoughlin-
OL,7,FBurke, instructed by solicitors at
OL,8,FPhoenix Law, told the court their
OL,9,Fintention to reply and said there were
OL,10,Flegal issues in the alleged offences
OL,11,Fwhich she said "merit" a second
OL,12,Fbarrister.
OL,14,FMr Gill was remanded in custody at
OL,15,FCloverhill Prison until the
OL,16,Fextradition hearing at the High Court
OL,17,Fin Dublin on April 21.
